arts.ttl: Norwich slip to five defeats in a row at Swansea as heat rises on Manning
arts.sum: Swansea piled the pressure on beleaguered Norwich boss Liam Manning as Zan Vipotnik's double secured a 2-1 Championship home win.

arts.ttl: Swansea vs Norwich predictions: Swans to heap more pressure on Canaries
arts.sum: Norwich boss Liam Manning could be one poor result away from the sack and Elliott Bretland is forecasting more Canaries misery as they face Swansea in south Wales.
